2a6e57347e722fa816878abb646721e312bca857.query: INSERT INTO projects (id, project) VALUES ($1, $2) RETURNING id

c246b6a26229dc61a3585ff27345639ed820e9dd.query: UPDATE projects SET project = project || CAST( $2 as JSONB) WHERE id = $1 RETURNING id

d1ca70f156e663001444e6252fdcc2f97b3fed16.query:
SELECT project AS "project: sqlx::types::Json<Project>"
        FROM projects
        WHERE project->>'owner' = $1 OR
        project->'viewers' ? $1 OR
        project->'members' ? $1

e095c0532f567775207992f3f873038bb748b455.query:
SELECT project as "project: sqlx::types::Json<Project>"
        FROM projects WHERE id = $1
